   "source": [
    "用指数的加减法替换乘法运算\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "a^x \\cdot a^y = a^{x+y}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\log(P_1 \\cdot P_2 \\cdot P_3) = \\log(P_1) + \\log(P_2) + \\log(P_3)\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7ad465b9-a6e9-400e-9d34-4963779bcae4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 对数查找表"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "de18ceae-4ee3-4a74-9e18-ce7c11f74392",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- 快速计算： 123.45 * 789.12\n",
    "    - 1.2345 * 10^2 * 7.8912 * 10^2 = 1.2345 * 7.8912 * 10^4\n",
    "    - log(123.45 * 789.12) = log(1.2345) + log(7.8912) + 4\n",
    "    - 查表"
   ]
  }
